      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/goldman-teams-up-with-blackstone-to-sell-novel-fund-finance-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 已与黑石集团 (Blackstone Inc.) 合作，将私募基金贷款打包成债券，这是一种新型债务形式，银行未来可能会考虑出售更多此类债务。]]></description>
